<div class="container login_join simple_auth connect-account">
	<div class="template-account__header">회원가입</div>
	<div class="template-account__wrapper join_page">
		<div class="template-account__left"></div>
      <%- include ("./menu/index.ejs",{state:2}) %>


			<div class="template-account__content">
            <div class="template-account__text_hdtype_1 alert title" style='display:none'>
               <div class="rte">
                  <p class='error'></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section" js-password-form="customerLoginForm">
               <div class='text-block align-center'>
                  <h2>회원가입</h2>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="progress section">
               <div class='progressbar'>
                  <div class='line'></div>
                  <ul>
                     <li class='active'>
                        <p> <span class='circle'></span>
                           <br> <span class='text'>간편인증</span> 
                        </p>
                     </li>
                     <li>
                        <p> <span class='circle'></span>
                           <br> <span class='text'>가입정보 입력</span> 
                        </p>
                     </li>
                     <li>
                        <p> <span class='circle'></span>
                           <br> <span class='text'>개인정보 동의</span> 
                        </p>
                     </li>
                  </ul>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class='line-block content-line'></div>
            <div class='section text'>
               <div class='text-block auth-title'>
                  <p>
                     기존에 hyundaipark을 아이디 또는 이메일로 사용중인 계정이 있습니다.<br><br>
                     기존의 계정에 로그인해서 SNS계정을 연결하시면, 하나의 계정으로 회원/주문 정보를 통합 관리할 수 있습니다.<br><br>                     
                     개인 계정 연결 및 해제는 마이페이지에서 가능합니다.
                  </p>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class='section'>
               <form method="post" action="#">
                  <div class=" label-block input-block id">
                     <label class="form-group__label subtitle-2 is-hidden" for="CustomerId">
                     </label>
                     <input id="CustomerId" autocapitalize="off" autocomplete="off" autofocus="" name="customer[id]" placeholder="아이디 또는 이메일" required="" spellcheck="false" type="text" data-need="id" data-need-length="10">
                  </div>
                  <div class=" label-block input-block password">
                     <label class="form-group__label subtitle-2 is-hidden" for="CustomerPassword">
                     </label>
                     <input id="CustomerBirthday" autocapitalize="off" autocomplete="off" autofocus="" name="customer[password]" placeholder="비밀번호" required="" spellcheck="false" type="password" data-need="password" data-need-length="10">
                  </div>
                  
               <div class="button-block connect-button loading-wrap">
                  <input class="button button--primary button--block button--large m-font-14" type="submit" value="연결하기" data-form-submit="doConnectButton">
                  <div class="loader">
                     <div class="smiley-spin">
                        <svg class="icon icon--medium icon__smiley" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8 15.5a7.5 7.5 0 110-15 7.5 7.5 0 010 15zm0-1a6.5 6.5 0 100-13 6.5 6.5 0 000 13zM4.947 9.776l-.894.448a4.413 4.413 0 007.894 0l-.894-.448a3.413 3.413 0 01-6.106 0zM9.5 5h1v2h-1V5zm-3 0h-1v2h1V5z"></path></svg>
                     </div>
                  </div>
               </div>

               </form>
            </div>

            
			</div>

	</div>
</div>